text: Volmer Otzen (3 October 1899 - 26 December 1979) was a Danish diver. He competed in the men's plain high diving event at the 1924 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1899 births Category:1979 deaths Category:Danish male divers Category:Olympic divers of Denmark Category:Divers at the 1924 Summer Olympics Category:Sportspeople from Copenhagen
